Package: alternc-mailpit
Priority: optional
Section: admin
Architecture: all
Depends: alternc (>= 3.5)
Description: Mailpit addon for AlternC
 AlternC is a mutualized hosting software manager for Linux.
 It allows you to manage your websites, domains, ftp, emails, aliases,
 web statistics, mailing-lists, etc.
 .
 This package is an optional module providing mailpit service, a mailcatcher
 for AlternC.
 .
 More information on https://www.alternc.com/ and https://mailpit.axllent.org/
